high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the clear bowl between the hand and knife.
Turn around and walk to the fridge so you are standing in front of it facing it.
Chill the bowl in the fridge on the middle shelf for a while then retrieve it and close the fridge.
Turn right and walk to the shelves on the wall.
Put the clear bowl to the left of the yellow item on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl on a shelf.

high_descs: head over to the kitchen counters on the right side of the kitchen
grab a bowl off of the kitchen counter
turn around and bring the bowl over to the fridge
place the bowl inside the fridge to cool off, then take it out
bring the cooled bowl over to the brown shelves in the corner of the kitchen
place the bowl on the middle brown shelf
anns.task_desc: place a cooled bowl on the shelves in the corner of the kitchen

high_descs: Turn around walk towards a white counter.
Pick up a glass bowl from the counter.
Turn around, then take a left and head towards a fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge, then remove it.
Turn to your right, and approach a set of shelves.
Place the bowl on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl on a shelf.
